WorkItem.Description:
Acidmaw Boots show up twice in the equipment comparison. Yes I am aware that the names are different for Alliance and Horde.  The Acidmaw Boots I am referring to are the Alliance Version and I do not know if this occurs for the Horde item as well.
 
One is the Acidmaw Boots [ http://www.wowhead.com/?item=47608 ] but the other is 245 Level Item with two gem slots  [ http://www.wowhead.com/?item=47919 ]
 
I disable the level 245 item for now but thought you guys would like to know about it for next release.
 
This is my 1st ever post. RAWR is an abolutely awesome tool. Irrespective of the complaints you receive, I have used this tool to become a much better player and provide a HUGE increase in DPS output.

Comments.Message: This is not a bug. There are both 258 and 245 versions of this pair of boots.
Would be neat to display the Itemlevel also in the Item-Tooltip.
